							<description>Research the [The First Ceiling] technology.</description>
						</value>
					</li>
					
					<li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
						<xpath>/Defs/AchievementsExpanded.AchievementDef[defName="SNS_Achievement_ResearchTech_Gen2_Ceiling_II"]/description</xpath>
						<value>
							<description>Research the [The Brink of Ascension] technology.</description>
